---
const pageTitle = "About - Astro Learning Project";

const identity = {
  firstName: "Juan",
  country: "Mexico",
  occupation: "Lerner",
  hobbies: ["basketball", "drawing", "reading"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React", "Astro"];

const happy = true;
const finished = false;
const goal = 3;

---


<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device--swidth">
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 30px;
            min-height: 70px;
            border-bottom: #77d3d4 3px solid;
        }
        header a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        header ul {
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }
        header li {
            display: inline;
            padding: 0 20px 0 20px;
        }
        header #branding {
            float: left;
        }
        header #branding h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        header nav {
            float: right;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        #main {
            padding: 30px;
            background: #fff;
        }
        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div id="branding">
                <h1>Astro Learning Project</h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blog/">Blog</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section id="main" class="container">
        <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
        <p>Hey there! Welcome to my Astro Learning Project! I am on a mission to conquer the universe of web development, one Astro component at a time. Think of this as my personal space odyssey, but with more code and fewer dramatic space rescues.</p>
        <p>I'm all about making learning fun and approachable. So, whether you're a fellow space cadet just starting out or a seasoned astronaut looking to brush up on your skills, you are in the right place. Lets boldly code where no one has coded before!</p>
        <h2>My Galactic Goals</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Create tutorials and guides that are out of this world (or at least easy to follow).</li>
            <li>Show off some stellar examples and projects to help you practice your Astro skills.</li>
            <li>Build a community where we can share our cosmic triumphs and tribulations.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>So, strap in and get ready for a fun-filled adventure through the Astro-verse. Together, we will navigate the stars of static site generation and have a blast doing it!</p>
        <p>Here are a few cosmic facts about me:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>My name is {identity.firstName}, but you can call me Captain Code.</li>
            <li>I live on planet {identity.country} and I work as an intergalactic {identity.occupation}.</li>
            {identity.hobbies.length >= 2 && (
                <li>When I'm not saving the galaxy, I enjoy {identity.hobbies[0]} and {identity.hobbies[1]}. Yes, even space heroes need hobbies!</li>
            )}
        </ul>
        <p>My stellar skills are:</p>
        <ul>
            {skills.map((skill) => <li>{skill}</li>)}
        </ul>

        {happy && <p>I am happy to be learning Astro!</p>}

        {finished && <p>I finished this tutorial!</p>}

        {goal === 3 ? <p>My goal is to finish in 3 days.</p> : <p>My goal is not 3 days.</p>}
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Astro Learning Project - To Infinity and Beyond!</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
